metadata.description: Original Coco is a collection of 10.000 randomly generated NFTs bringing SALSA to the Ethereum Blockchain. Cocos have a variety of different original attributes (200+) that include faces, outﬁts and special objects. All Cocos are OG but some are more rare than others. There are 10 special edition Cocos, complete outﬁt Cocos and subtribes like ninjas and bikers. A community based project in which each Coco holder gets a vote to participate in decision taking and access to OG events including airdrops and giveaways. Cocos are not pets, they´re OG. Visit https://www.originalcocos.io/ to know more!
metadata.name: Original Cocos
